metadata.name: Psychedelic Dream
metadata.description:
First of the BioMaiden series! "Psychedelic Dream" is a drawing of a lady in a psychedelic state of mind. I wanted to show the psychedelic experience with lots of colorful flowing movement and patterns. The mind is expanding with limitless potential, yet this could all be just a dream...

Dimensions: 1200 x 1200 px
Resolution: 150 dpi
